data.name: label20.ToolTipText
data.value: This is the name of the C64 gameslist (essentially a Platform created by C64Dreams). By default this is "Games" but some may have changed this name. If so, enter the new 'Platform' name here. Be precise. Note: untested feature.

data.name: label5.ToolTipText
data.value: This should point to the root "C64 Dreams" Directory. This directory also contains a directory of the same name, so be careful. You'll know you're in the right one if you can see Launcbox.exe in there and NOT Configurator.exe.
